    rdfs:label "Data steward"@en ;
    dctm:source "Strengholt, Piethein. Data Management at Scale: Modern Data Architecture with Data Mesh and Data Fabric. O’Reilly Media (Kindle Edition), pp. 369–371."@en ;
    skos:definition "Helps ensure that data policies and standards are followed; often serves as a subject matter expert for a specific type of data."@en ;
